translation.Name: Rio Note - Military #1
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_2: Due to the Exterminators attack, we need to repair the fences immediately. We've lost 1 APC and 2 armored offroaders, and 1 damaged Ural, and, apparently, some of our supplies were stolen.
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_3: Now about human losses, we've lost 5 men, but the majority of the raiders were also taken down, including their leader.
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_4: We expect for repairs to start soon.
